'''Vidge''' was a tall, pale [[Langhesi]] [[Gender/Legends|male]] who was living on [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]] during the waning [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. In [[29 BBY/Legends|29 BBY]], he was the chief shaper of a shipbuilding team that grew and formed [[Sekotan Personal Starship]]s from [[seed-partner]]s. He had large, wet [[Eye/Legends|eyes]] and his [[Clothing/Legends|clothes]] were wet and sprinkled with bits of glowing [[Slime/Legends|slime]].

